description:
Roll a 1d7 at the beginning of each enemy army's phase to determine which condition to apply to the nearest unit from that army within five spaces until the end of the phase:
 1=@{condition}{Vulnerable}{[Vulnerable]}
@{style}{italic}{The enemy’s armor has an easily-seen opening.}
 2=@{condition}{Hexed}{[Hexed]}
@{style}{italic}{The enemy fumbles their weapon.}
 3=@{condition}{Poisoned}{[Posioned]}
@{style}{italic}{The enemy ate some bad food before coming here.}
 4=@{condition}{Shocked}{[Shocked]}
@{style}{italic}{A bolt of lightning comes down from the heavens to strike this one particular enemy.}
 5=@{condition}{Chilled}{[Chilled]}
@{style}{italic}{A sudden, bone-chilling breeze hits the enemy.}
 6=@{condition}{Distorted}{[Distorted]}
@{style}{italic}{The enemy has trouble summoning their magic, if they use it.}
 7=Apply no condition.
@{style}{italic}{The enemy sneezes. Nothing else happens.}
